Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.90,0:00:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道你肯定會來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.43,0:00:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟沒有我在你就辦不成事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.58,0:00:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.71,0:00:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.96,0:00:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你變強了 史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這導師可真熱衷於工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
